        <p>  Visiting temples is integral, with rituals like Abhishekam (holy bath for idols) and Archana (chanting prayers for devotees).</p>
        <h4>Pilgrimages:</h4>
        <p>  Tirumala Venkateswara Temple in Tirupati is a major pilgrimage site.</p>
        <h4>Offering Prasadam:</h4>
        <p>Devotees offer food, fruits, and coconuts to deities, later distributed as prasadam.</p>
